title: Appointments to Hospital Authority
content_text: The two serving members reappointed are Professor Francis Chan Ka-leung and Ms Anita Cheng Wai-ching while the new member appointed is Mr Quinton Lam Chun-ki. Mr Lam is an Advanced Practice Nurse in the public healthcare sector. He currently serves in the Department of Surgery of Pamela Youde Nethersole Eastern Hospital. The Secretary for Food and Health, Professor Sophia Chan, welcomed Mr Lam to the HA. She also thanked Mr Ho Wing-yin, who will retire from the HA with effect from April 1, 2018, for his advice and contribution to the HA over the years.  The
